{"id":116,"date":"2016-01-17T18:30:00","date_gmt":"2016-01-18T02:30:00","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/murphlaw.net\/?page_id=116"},"modified":"2023-10-02T11:15:36","modified_gmt":"2023-10-02T18:15:36","slug":"personal-injury-attorney-los-angeles-ca","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/areas-of-expertise\/personal-injury-attorney-los-angeles-ca\/","title":{"rendered":"Personal Injury"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"pl-116\" class=\"panel-layout\">\n<div id=\"pg-116-0\" class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\">\n<div id=\"pgc-116-0-0\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\" data-weight=\"1\">\n<h2 id=\"panel-116-0-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-headline panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"0\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\" wp-image-149 alignleft\" src=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/01\/PI.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"518\" height=\"362\" srcset=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/01\/PI.jpg 600w, https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/01\/PI-300x210.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 518px) 100vw, 518px\" \/>Personal Injury\/Wrongful Death Attorneys:  Fresno &amp; Fresnno County<\/h2>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"pg-116-1\" class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\">\n<div id=\"pgc-116-1-0\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\" data-weight=\"0.5\">\n<div id=\"panel-116-1-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"1\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\">\n<div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n<p>Personal injuries are more common than many think. According to the CDC, over 1 million people suffer from burns each year and over 1 million people go to the emergency room for slip and fall accidents every year.<\/p>\n<p>We\u2019re at risk for personal injury anywhere we go. In fact, the most common forms of personal injury occur from automobile accidents, workplace incidents, criminal activity, and product liability.<\/p>\n<p>If you or a loved one has suffered a personal injury or wrongful death, don\u2019t hesitate to call the <a href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/about-us\/\">Chuckstern Murphy Law Firm<\/a>. We serve clients in the  Fresno and Fresno County areas, including  Fresno, Westlake, Thousand Oaks, Camarillo, Burbank, and Newbury Park.<\/p>\n<p>Our attorneys specialize in personal injury law and wrongful death cases, which include cases from car accidents to catastrophic injuries and death.<\/p>\n<p>Our Fresno County and  Fresno personal injury lawyers care deeply about our clients&#8217; well-being and health and will fight vigorously to recoup all medical expenses, pain and suffering, and emotional distress sustained as a result of your injury.<\/p>\n<p>Our law firm has been involved in complex multi-million dollar personal injury and wrongful death lawsuits. But we pride ourselves on helping the little guy. See how our personal injury attorneys can help you get the compensation and justice you deserve.<\/p>\n<h2>Personal Injuries May Be Debilitating<\/h2>\n<p>Personal injuries may affect your income and leave you unable to enjoy the things you love most out of life. Unintentional accidents remain the third leading cause of death in the US.<\/p>\n<p>Dealing with a personal injury or wrongful death to a loved one may be scary, especially without experienced help on your side. If you\u2019re in the  Fresno and Fresno areas, understand that there is an experienced team of experts who can help you win your case.<\/p>\n<p>We will deal with insurance adjusters and fight any opposing litigation by any company or individual who attempts to deny your claim.<\/p>\n<p>Trust, resilience, and intuition compromise our law firm\u2019s grit, as well as our goal-oriented approach to helping our clients claim the justice that they deserve.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"pg-116-2\" class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-ratio-direction=\"right\">\n<div id=\"pgc-116-2-0\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\" data-weight=\"1\">\n<div id=\"panel-116-2-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"3\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\">\n<div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n<h2>Personal Injury Cases We Handle<\/h2>\n<p>While most think of personal injuries as falling off a ladder at work or slipping on the sidewalk, you\u2019re actually protected for a lot more than you may think.<\/p>\n<p>The following is a list of the personal injury and wrongful death lawsuits that we handle:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Dog Bite Accidents<\/li>\n<li>Bicycle Accidents<\/li>\n<li>Motorcycle Crashes<\/li>\n<li>Car Accidents<\/li>\n<li>Truck Accidents<\/li>\n<li>Heavy Haul Accidents<\/li>\n<li>Bus Accidents<\/li>\n<li>Catastrophic Injuries<\/li>\n<li>Wrongful Death<\/li>\n<li>Dangerous Conditions of Public Property<\/li>\n<li>Premises Liability\/Slip and Fall Accidents<\/li>\n<li>Bar Fights<\/li>\n<li>Construction Site Accidents<\/li>\n<li>Assault &amp; Battery<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>Providing Compensation for a Wrongful Death Suit<\/h2>\n<p>Wrongful deaths can be the result of a number of factors, including medical malpractice, unintentional injury, and criminal activity. Not only are wrongful deaths devastating emotionally, but they can also be devastating financially.<\/p>\n<p>At Chuckstern Murphy Law Firm, we provide victims\u2019 families the support they need to navigate through an emotionally exhausting trial. We get to the root cause of wrongful deaths and file a claim that holds the proper parties responsible.<\/p>\n<p>Know that you have a trusted team of personal injury attorneys on your side.<\/p>\n<h2>You Always Have a Right to a Claim<\/h2>\n<p>Whether you suffer from a pre-existing condition or don\u2019t have insurance for a particular accident, it doesn\u2019t mean you\u2019re not entitled to compensation.<\/p>\n<p>For years we\u2019ve represented clients in a variety of claims ranging from multimillion-dollar claims to smaller accidents. No matter what the scenario, we work with our clients to protect their interests and give them the justice they deserve.<\/p>\n<p>People choose our law firm because we win big for our clients. Find out how we can help you by calling our <a href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/contact-us\/fresno-office\/\"> Fresno office<\/a> at 415-217-9456 or our <a href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/contact-us\/westlake-village-office\/\">Fresno office<\/a> at 415-217-9456. Or, <a href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/contact-us\/fresno-office\/\">sign up for a free consultation online<\/a> or contact us online at our  Fresno or Fresno offices.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Personal Injury\/Wrongful Death Attorneys:  Fresno &amp; Fresnno County Personal injuries are more common than many think. According to the CDC, over 1 million people suffer from burns each year and over 1 million people go to the emergency room for slip and fall accidents every year. We\u2019re at risk for personal injury anywhere we go. In fact, the most common forms of personal injury occur from automobile accidents, workplace incidents, criminal activity, and product liability. If you or a loved one has suffered a personal injury or wrongful death, don